943
00:58:22,180 --> 00:58:24,180
We're not lying.

944
00:58:24,180 --> 00:58:25,180
It's true.

945
00:58:25,180 --> 00:58:26,180
Enough.

946
00:58:26,180 --> 00:58:28,180
Now, investigate and watch Alfa.

947
00:58:28,180 --> 00:58:30,180
Hurry.

948
00:58:30,180 --> 00:58:31,180
Yes, Sir.

949
00:58:31,180 --> 00:58:34,180
Teleportation.

950
00:58:34,180 --> 00:58:38,180
Please.

951
00:58:38,180 --> 00:58:40,180
Please come in.

952
00:58:40,180 --> 00:58:44,180
This is my house.

953
00:58:44,180 --> 00:58:45,180
It's a nice house.

954
00:58:45,180 --> 00:58:47,180
It's clean and neat.

955
00:58:47,180 --> 00:58:48,180
Yes, Sir.

956
00:58:48,180 --> 00:58:49,180
It's nice.

957
00:58:49,180 --> 00:58:51,180
Thank you.

958
00:58:51,180 --> 00:58:56,180
