966
00:59:10,180 --> 00:59:11,180
Yes, Sir.

967
00:59:11,180 --> 00:59:14,180
Be careful.

968
00:59:14,180 --> 00:59:22,180
Don't be so sad.

969
00:59:22,180 --> 00:59:23,180
Remember.

970
00:59:23,180 --> 00:59:25,180
She's my wife.

971
00:59:25,180 --> 00:59:31,180
Get in.

972
