975
00:59:48,180 --> 00:59:50,180
Where is she?

976
00:59:50,180 --> 00:59:52,180
She's gone.

977
00:59:52,180 --> 00:59:54,180
Wait.

978
00:59:54,180 --> 00:59:57,180
Don't tell me.

979
00:59:57,180 --> 00:59:58,180
Alfa...

