986
01:00:20,180 --> 01:00:21,180
Do you agree?

987
01:00:21,180 --> 01:00:23,180
I agree.

988
01:00:24,180 --> 01:00:30,180
Then, a kind-hearted warrior came to save the princess.

989
01:00:30,180 --> 01:00:35,180
