992
01:00:43,180 --> 01:00:50,180
Alfa.

993
01:00:50,180 --> 01:00:52,180
Why are you crying?

994
01:00:53,180 --> 01:00:55,180
I'm sorry.

995
01:00:55,180 --> 01:01:02,180
I still can't believe...

996
01:01:02,180 --> 01:01:06,180
