997
01:01:06,180 --> 01:01:10,180
But I'm happy.

998
01:01:10,180 --> 01:01:12,180
I'm so happy.

999
01:01:12,180 --> 01:01:16,180
I'll try to stop time.

1000
01:01:16,180 --> 01:01:19,180
I'll always be with you.

1001
01:01:20,180 --> 01:01:22,180
Be patient, honey.

1002
01:01:22,180 --> 01:01:26,180
Your father and I will try to do that.

1003
01:01:26,180 --> 01:01:32,180
Mom.

1004
01:01:32,180 --> 01:01:37,180
When can I meet my friends?

1005
01:01:37,180 --> 01:01:40,180
Not yet, Alfa.

1006
01:01:40,180 --> 01:01:44,180
