1011
01:02:32,180 --> 01:02:35,180
The Fatang Blaster.

1012
01:02:35,180 --> 01:02:39,180
This is better.

1013
01:02:39,180 --> 01:02:41,180
It's time to sleep.

1014
01:02:41,180 --> 01:02:44,180
It's safe.

1015
01:02:44,180 --> 01:02:59,180
I can't sleep.

1016
01:02:59,180 --> 01:03:03,180
I was going to sleep on my head, but now I'm sleeping on my feet.

1017
01:03:03,180 --> 01:03:06,180
I'll remember this.

1018
01:03:06,180 --> 01:03:09,180
I'll wake up and everything will be fine.

1019
01:03:09,180 --> 01:03:11,180
I won't give up.

1020
01:03:11,180 --> 01:03:14,180
(Alfa's room)

1021
01:03:14,180 --> 01:03:36,180
Panji.

1022
01:03:36,180 --> 01:03:38,180
This must be you.

1023
01:03:38,180 --> 01:03:41,180
Open it.

1024
01:03:41,180 --> 01:03:44,180
I'm sorry, Sir.

1025
01:03:44,180 --> 01:03:48,180
You'll be a ghost when you sleep.

1026
01:03:48,180 --> 01:03:50,180
You're a ghost.

1027
01:03:50,180 --> 01:03:52,180
I'll make you pay.

1028
01:03:52,180 --> 01:03:55,180
Good morning, Sir.

1029
01:03:55,180 --> 01:03:58,180
Alfa.

1030
01:03:58,180 --> 01:03:59,180
What are you doing?

1031
01:03:59,180 --> 01:04:03,180
