1032
01:04:03,180 --> 01:04:05,180
A little exercise.

1033
01:04:05,180 --> 01:04:08,180
To start the Fatang Blaster.

1034
01:04:08,180 --> 01:04:11,180
Please enjoy this.

1035
01:04:11,180 --> 01:04:18,180
I'll pour you a drink.

1036
01:04:18,180 --> 01:04:33,180
Sir.

1037
01:04:33,180 --> 01:04:35,180
Here.

1038
01:04:35,180 --> 01:04:55,180
Sir.

1039
01:04:55,180 --> 01:05:02,180
It's okay.

1040
01:05:02,180 --> 01:05:05,180
