It's at Duyung.

1064
01:06:26,180 --> 01:06:28,180
Duyung?

1065
01:06:28,180 --> 01:06:30,180
Yes.

1066
01:06:30,180 --> 01:06:32,180
Duyung.

1067
01:06:32,180 --> 01:06:36,180
What is that?

1068
01:06:36,180 --> 01:06:38,180
Yes.

1069
01:06:38,180 --> 01:06:40,180
It's a sign of good news.

1070
01:06:40,180 --> 01:06:43,180
Alfa is happy.

1071
01:06:43,180 --> 01:06:45,180
What is it?

1072
01:06:45,180 --> 01:06:47,180
Alfa.

1073
