1095
01:07:38,180 --> 01:07:39,180
Yes.

1096
01:07:39,180 --> 01:07:40,180
You're happy, right?

1097
01:07:40,180 --> 01:07:41,180
What's wrong?

1098
01:07:41,180 --> 01:07:43,180
I'll tell you later.

1099
01:07:43,180 --> 01:07:44,180
